---
import BrowserFrame from './BrowserFrame.astro';
---

<section class="section-pad" id="showcase">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="kicker">A closer look</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Designed to feel <span class="accent">calm and clear</span></h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Every screen is built around the same idea: surface what matters, hide what doesn't, and get out of your way.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="show-row reverse reveal">
      <div class="show-text">
        <span class="show-badge" style="background:rgba(245,158,11,0.16);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.4);color:#fcd34d"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 2h4"/><circle cx="12" cy="14" r="8"/></svg> Focus mode</span>
        <h3>A Pomodoro timer that keeps you in flow</h3>
        <p>Start a session and the whole tab quiets down to a single ring counting your focus. Pair it with a quote for the mindset you need right now.</p>
        <ul class="show-list">
          <li><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Customizable work and break intervals</li>
          <li><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Pause, resume, and skip without losing your place</li>
          <li><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Ambient soundscapes and YouTube focus music while you work</li>
          <li><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Session count rolls into your insights</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="show-media">
        <BrowserFrame src="/images/pomodoro.png" alt="Cuewise Pomodoro timer in Glass mode" label="Pomodoro" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="show-row reveal">
      <div class="show-text">
        <span class="show-badge" style="background:rgba(59,130,246,0.16);border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.4);color:#93c5fd"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16"/><path d="M18 17V9M13 17V5M8 17v-3"/></svg> Progress</span>
        <h3>Insights that celebrate your momentum</h3>
        <p>See your current streak, goals completed and the categories of wisdom you return to most. Encouraging by design — these numbers cheer you on.</p>
        <ul class="show-list">
          <li><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Streaks, goals and focus sessions at a glance</li>
          <li><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Category breakdown across all ten themes</li>
          <li><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Daily, weekly and monthly trends when you want to go deeper</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="show-media">
        <BrowserFrame src="/images/insights.png" alt="Cuewise insights dashboard in Glass mode" label="Insights" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="show-row reverse reveal">
      <div class="show-text">
        <span class="show-badge" style="background:rgba(139,92,246,0.16);border:1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.4);color:#c4b5fd"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 2v8l3-3 3 3V2"/><path d="M4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2H20v20H6.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H20"/></svg> Your collection</span>
        <h3>Curate a library of quotes that move you</h3>
        <p>Browse, search and filter a hundred-plus quotes — or add your own. Favorite the keepers, hide the rest, and see which ones you return to most.</p>
        <ul class="show-list">
          <li><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Search by text, author or category</li>
          <li><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Add unlimited custom quotes and group them into collections</li>
          <li><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Favorites and hidden, fully under your control</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="show-media">
        <BrowserFrame src="/images/quotes.png" alt="Cuewise quote management library in Glass mode" label="Quotes" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
